Text: She is one of the biggest Dallas Cowboys fans I ever met. If you can respond to this tweet I will send it to her. I know it would make her day.I ask this from the bottom of my hart pls. Send her a video, her name is Jenni Landeros. Thank you for your time. God Bless!

@EzekielElliott
 I'm sending this tweet to you ask the team for a favor. If the team can make video from my cousin Jenni. She has been fighting the battle with cancer for a while. Doctors don't know how much longer she will last. If the boys could do this for her it'd be awesome.
